2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_cmat_sarahdoyle_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_cmat_sarahdoyle_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_cmat_sarahdoyle_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_cmat_sarahdoyle_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/2025_cmat_sarahdoyle_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cmat">CMAT</a>宣布了一张新专辑，并分享了令人振奋的单曲“ Running/Planning”  - 请查看下面的所有详细信息。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cmat-brits-interview-last-dinner-party-inspiring-women-sam-fender-new-music-3842738">CMAT说，最后一个晚宴上正在标志着女性在独立场景中的新时代：“这让我的心唱歌”</a><br /></strong></li></ul><p>这张唱片是她2023 LP的后续记录“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/cmat-crazymad-for-me-review-lyrics-tracklist-3512398">Crazymad，For Me</a> ”，将于8月29日发行，可以<a href="https://cmat.ffm.to/EURO-COUNTRY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>预订/预先保存。今天（3月25日）共享了LP的第一个Taster，即“跑步/计划”，您可以收听并查看下面单曲的视频。</p><p> CMAT  - 真实姓名Ciara Mary-Alice Thompson  - 还宣布了一套新的英国/爱尔兰和欧洲巡回演唱会，其中包括10月2日在O2 Brixton Academy举行的演出，并将在12月3日在都柏林的3arena结束。</p><p>门票将于4月4日BST上午10点进行英国约会，可以<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcmat-tickets%2Fartist%2F5345253" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买，而粉丝可以在4月1日下午5点之前预订新专辑，从而<a href="https://cmat.ffm.to/EURO-COUNTRY" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处</a>购买门票。该票的门票将于<a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fcmat-tickets%2Fartist%2F5345253" target="_blank" rel="noopener">第二天</a>（4月2日）上午10点开始销售。她的欧洲日期现在<a href="https://cmatbaby.com/live/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在这里</a>出售。 </p><p><iframe title="Spotify嵌入：跑步/计划" style="border-radius: 12px" width="100%" height="352" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/album/31gACQVSidtVeFzL4hUGy2?si=HMqsmQd5QXKU1up9wuGz2g&#038;nd=1&#038;dlsi=01377aee960844f4&#038;utm_source=oembed"></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="CMAT-跑步/计划（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hAvWMb-zoKM?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在谈到她的新单曲时，CMAT说：“&#39;跑步/计划&#39;是关于必须追逐自己的尾巴才能足够好才能存在。这是对女性社会压力的抽象观点 - 特别是通过关系镜头：您开始与某人约会，您要订婚，结婚，您就结婚了，您有孩子等等……一切都必须遵循这种线性模式。</p><p> “当您不遵循这条道路的那一刻，您的妈妈就开始向您发出。每个人都应该走的狭窄道路……当您走到这一点之外的那一刻，它会感到非常压力。我不认识任何人喜欢，&#39;是的，爱这个！</p><p>至于专辑本身，CMAT将其描述为“我做过的最好的东西”。 </p><p><img decoding="async" src="https://mcusercontent.com/4874fac40102c3d5f5a3a97f0/images/05c6438f-657e-a65e-3ce9-30dfbddf426b.jpg" /></p><p>她补充说：“记录这是我为自己创造的最重要的唱片的一半……主要是因为这让我发疯。</p><p> “我总是要做我想做的工作，因为我的脑海里有些格里姆林告诉我是否狗屎。除了成功之外，还有一个更大的gremlin希望我使音乐变得非常好。她有时很残酷，有时毁了我的生活，但她是我生活的守护者，而且她总是对的。”</p><p>这位爱尔兰歌手兼词曲作者<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cmat-brits-interview-last-dinner-party-inspiring-women-sam-fender-new-music-3842738">最近谈到</a><em><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cmat-brits-interview-last-dinner-party-inspiring-women-sam-fender-new-music-3842738">NME</a></em>时说：“有很多新音乐，很快就会出现。我花了整个9月至12月在纽约市的一个洞中工作。现在已经完成了。我在那里失去了一定的想法，但听起来很棒，”她说。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="英国人2025：CMAT谈论新音乐的计划和即将与Sam Fender进行的巡回演出" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/bzNPu4lnv4o?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “我真的很专注于将现场音乐传递到现场音乐的歌曲，因为我的现场乐队是我所做的事情的重要组成部分。它们是我成为英国一个知名人士的基础，他能够出售演出门票。如果不是我的乐队，我将无法做到这一点，所以我为他们和他们写了一张专辑来杀死他们和我杀害。”</p><h3> <strong>CMAT将播放：</strong></h3><p><strong>七月<br />12  -  NOS，里斯本</strong><br /><strong>26  - 牛津郡卡车节</strong><br /><strong>27  - 谢菲尔德电车节</strong><br /><strong><br />八月<br />1  - 贝拉德鲁姆塔尔坦心脏，贝拉德鲁姆</strong><br /><strong>2  - 现在在一起，沃特福德</strong><br /><strong>7  -  Syd for Solen，哥本哈根</strong><br /><strong>8  - 哥德堡向西走的路</strong><br /><strong>14  -  Cabaret Vert，Charleville Mezieres</strong><br /> <strong>15  - 低地，投标人</strong><br /><strong>16  -  Crickhowell的绿人节</strong></p><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>2  -  O2 Academy Brixton，伦敦</strong><br /><strong>4  - 学院，曼彻斯特</strong><br /><strong>5  -  O2学院，利兹</strong><br /><strong>6  -  NX，纽卡斯尔</strong><br /><strong>9  - 格拉斯哥巴罗兰舞厅</strong><br /><strong>12  - 洛克城，诺丁汉</strong><br /><strong>13  - 玉米交换，剑桥</strong><br /><strong>15  - 布莱顿圆顶音乐厅</strong><br /><strong>16  - 伯明翰O2研究所</strong><br /><strong>17  -  UEA，英国诺里奇</strong><br /><strong>19  - 八角形，谢菲尔德</strong><br /><strong>20  -  O2学院，布里斯托尔</strong><br /><strong><br />十二月<br />5  -  3arena，都柏林</strong></p><p>在此之前，她将支持<a href="/artists/sam-fender">萨姆·芬德（Sam Fender）</a>进行<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sam-fender-announces-huge-summer-2025-uk-stadium-shows-buy-tickets-3814931">一系列英国约会</a>，她将于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2025-line-up-announced-headliners-tickets-3843426">6月27日星期五</a>参加<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2025">2025年格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cmat-announces-new-album-euro-country-with-new-single-running-planning-and-huge-uk-and-european-tour-3849181">CMAT帖子宣布了新专辑“ Euro-Country”，其中包括新单曲“ Running/Planning”和巨大的英国和欧洲巡回演唱</a>会在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首次出现。</p> ;
 Z世代更喜欢在社交媒体上观看影响者而不是电影和电视，研究节目https://www.nme.com/news/gen-z-prefer-watching-influencers-on-social-media-to-film-and-pilm-and-wilm-and-tv-study-shows-3849177？ source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = gen-z-z-prefer-tofter-tofter-tofluencer-inflearcer-in-social-media-to-to-to-to-to-to-to-to-tv-study-showsAneesa Ahmed Tue, 25 Mar 2025 20:20:36 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV NewsEntertainmentTV https://www.nme.com/?p=3849177 <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="社交媒体图标应用。信用-Jonathan Raa/Nurphoto通过Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这一代人的时间也比普通人看电视和电影的时间少26％</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gen-z-prefer-watching-influencers-on-social-media-to-film-and-tv-study-shows-3849177">Z世代更喜欢在社交媒体上观看影响者而不是电影和电视，研究节目</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1240" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="社交媒体图标应用。信用-Jonathan Raa/Nurphoto通过Getty Images" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Social-media-icon-applications.-Credit-Jonathan-Raa_NurPhoto-via-Getty-Images-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> Z世代更喜欢在社交媒体上观看有影响力的人和创作者驱动的，而不是电影和电视等大型预算<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/entertainment">娱乐</a>。</p><p>根据调查，ZS一代和43％的千禧一代中有56％的人发现社交媒体内容“比传统的电视节目和电影更相关”，其中一半说他们在电影和电视上对社交媒体人物的个人联系更强。</p><p> <a href="https://www2.deloitte.com/us/en/insights/industry/technology/digital-media-trends-consumption-habits-survey/2025.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">德勤（Deloitte）进行的</a>数字媒体趋势调查向消费者询问了他们的媒体消费习惯。它还评估了他们花费了多少时间消耗不同形式的媒体，并发现Z世代花费的时间多54％，或大约50分钟，而不是每天在社交平台上的平均消费者。这一代人的时间还要少26％（每天少44分钟），而不是看电视和电影的普通人。</p><p>德勤有限责任公司副主席中国维德纳（China Widener）告诉<a href="https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/business/business-news/deloitte-gen-z-creator-content-streaming-price-1236171227/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">好莱坞记者</a>：“想想当今，传统媒体和社交媒体之间存在的人们的注意力和时间的战争。因此，当您只是在他们花费时间的情况下考虑这两种服务类型时，您只是在使用这两种服务的情况下？ </p><figure id="attachment_3849189" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3849189" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3849189" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Various-media-libraries-and-streaming-services-on-a-TV.-Credit-Bernd-Weisbrod_picture-alliance-via-Getty-Image-min.jpg" alt="电视上的各种媒体库和流媒体服务。信用-BerndWeißbrod/图片联盟通过Getty" width="2000" height="1240" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Various-media-libraries-and-streaming-services-on-a-TV.-Credit-Bernd-Weisbrod_picture-alliance-via-Getty-Image-min.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Various-media-libraries-and-streaming-services-on-a-TV.-Credit-Bernd-Weisbrod_picture-alliance-via-Getty-Image-min-400x248.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Various-media-libraries-and-streaming-services-on-a-TV.-Credit-Bernd-Weisbrod_picture-alliance-via-Getty-Image-min-800x496.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Various-media-libraries-and-streaming-services-on-a-TV.-Credit-Bernd-Weisbrod_picture-alliance-via-Getty-Image-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Various-media-libraries-and-streaming-services-on-a-TV.-Credit-Bernd-Weisbrod_picture-alliance-via-Getty-Image-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Various-media-libraries-and-streaming-services-on-a-TV.-Credit-Bernd-Weisbrod_picture-alliance-via-Getty-Image-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3849189" class="wp-caption-text">电视上的各种媒体库和流媒体服务。信用 - 通过Getty的BerndWeißbrod/图片联盟</figcaption></figure><p>根据Deloitte的调查，朝着社交媒体人格驱动的内容如此受欢迎的另一个引起的因素是与他们的“个人联系”。某些创作者的粉丝可能会与他们建立副社会关系，从而使参与度保持较高。</p><p>去年，一项研究发现， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/smartphone-now-most-used-screen-for-watching-new-video-content-3775590">智能手机现在是电视前观看新视频内容的“最常用屏幕”</a> 。</p><p>使用Hub Entertainment Research分析的数据的一份<a href="https://variety.com/vip/youtube-tiktok-eroding-viewing-time-spent-streaming-tv-movies-1236069015/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>特别</i></a>报告表明，手机屏幕已成为观看视频的首次选择屏幕，在连接电视之前，一个百分点。</p><p>例如，Tiktok用户观看视频内容的平均小时数已从2022年的2.12增加到2024年的2.48，而Instagram， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/facebook">Facebook</a>和YouTube也证明了类似的增加。</p><p> 2024年的<em>综艺</em>报道强调，电视节目和电影现在占13-24岁的屏幕时间的32％，而35岁以上的观众则为59％。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gen-z-prefer-watching-influencers-on-social-media-to-film-and-tv-study-shows-3849177">Z世代更喜欢在社交媒体上观看影响者而不是电影和电视，研究节目</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 CMA警告https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-may-have-breach-the-the-law-and-misled-fans-fans-during-oasis-oasis-oasis-reunion-tour-tour-tour-tir-tiket-sale-cma-warns-3849182?u tm_source = rss＆utm_medium = rss＆utm_campaign = ticketmaster-may-have-have-the-law the-law and-missled-nir-oasis-oasis-oasis-rounion-reunion-tour-tour-tour-tour-tour-tour-tir-cale-cma-warnsMax Pilley Tue, 25 Mar 2025 20:04:36 +0000 Music NewsNewsBritpop https://www.nme.com/?p=3849182 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>竞争和市场管理局正在代表英国政府调查有争议的“ Oasis Live” 25&#39;门票销售过程</p><p>CMA在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上首先出现<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-may-have-breached-the-law-and-misled-fans-during-oasis-reunion-tour-ticket-sale-cma-warns-3849182">在Oasis Reunion Tour Tick出售期间，邮票票务员可能“违反了法律”和“误导粉丝”</a> 。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/noel_liam_oasis-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>竞争和市场管理局（CMA）警告说，在去年夏天的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">OASIS</a>门票拍卖中，Ticketmaster可能已经“违反法律”和“误导粉丝”。 </p><ul><li data-leveltext="" data-font="Symbol" data-listid="1060" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559683&quot;:0,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-posinset="1" data-aria-level="1"><b>阅读更多：</b><b> </b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/oasis-reunion-liam-noel-gallagher-3787549"><b>您必须滚动它：通往绿洲的岩石之路</b></a></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/uk-government-price-cap-ticket-touts-secondary-dynamic-consultation-chris-bryant-interview-3827671">英国政府在一月份向门票再销售市场发起了磋商，</a>目的是“更好地保护球迷，改善现场活动的机会并支持英国世界领先的现场活动领域的发展”。</p><p>该咨询是 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-fans-react-to-ticketmasters-dynamic-pricing-3789361">在去年夏天围绕Oasis Live &#39;25售票销售的争议</a>之后的，因为由于需求而无需警告而导致门票成本似乎激增，因此数千名粉丝激怒了。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-cma-launches-official-government-enquiry-into-dynamic-surge-ticket-pricing-3790957">CMA</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-european-commission-reportedly-investigating-dynamic-pricing-amid-oasis-tickets-controversy-3790240">欧洲委员会</a>都在调查这个问题。</p><p>此外， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-are-preparing-to-cancel-more-than-50000-tickets-sold-via-secondary-ticket-sites-3807274">Oasis和Ticketmaster在10月宣布，他们计划取消50,000多张通过非注册二级售票网站出售的旅行票</a>。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/thousands-of-oasis-tickets-are-now-being-cancelled-by-ticketmaster-in-bot-crackdown-but-many-fans-are-unhappy-3836142#:~:text=fans%20are%20unhappy-,Thousands%20of%20Oasis%20tickets%20are%20now%20being%20cancelled%20by%20Ticketmaster,but%20many%20fans%20are%20unhappy&amp;text=Thousands%20of%20tickets%20to%20this,they%20have%20been%20targeted%20wrongfully.">该过程在2月开始采取行动</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3793637" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3793637" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3793637 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-ticketmaster-matt-cardy-1.jpg" alt="绿洲" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-ticketmaster-matt-cardy-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-ticketmaster-matt-cardy-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-ticketmaster-matt-cardy-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-ticketmaster-matt-cardy-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-ticketmaster-matt-cardy-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/oasis-ticketmaster-matt-cardy-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3793637" class="wp-caption-text"> OASIS Ticketmaster页面。学分：马特·卡迪（Matt Cardy）/盖蒂（Getty）</figcaption></figure><p>现在， <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/news/cma-seeks-changes-to-the-way-ticketmaster-labels-tickets-and-provides-pricing-information-to-fans" target="_blank" rel="noopener">CMA已经对Ticketmaster进行了调查</a>，称他们担心该公司可能以两种关键方式“违反了消费者保护法”。</p><p>首先，他们说Ticketmaster将某些座位的门票标记为“铂金”，并以“几乎是同等标准票的价格的2.5倍，而没有充分解释他们没有提供额外的好处，并且通常位于体育场的同一地区”。他们声称这有可能给客户带来误导性的印象，即白金门票比标准票更好。</p><p>其他潜在的违反法律涉及Ticketmaster并未告知消费者以不同的价格有两类票。它补充说，所有便宜的门票在发布更昂贵的门票之前首先出售，这导致顾客在等待长时间的情况下不了解他们必须支付更多费用。</p><p> CMA补充说，尽管所谓的“动态定价”在绿洲销售中得到了广泛报道的影响，在绿洲销售中，门票价格根据需求水平实时波动，但他们“没有发现证据表明是这种情况”。取而代之的是，他们说Ticketmaster首先发布了较低的价格票，一旦售罄，就开始出售价格较高的门票。</p><p>他们补充说：“ CMA担心消费者没有明确，及时的信息有关站立票的定价如何工作。” “尤其是许多客户不得不等待冗长的排队才能查看可用的门票”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3800092" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800092" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800092" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement.jpg" alt="绿洲的利亚姆和诺埃尔·加拉格尔" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/OasisAustralian-tour-dates-announcement-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800092" class="wp-caption-text"> Oasis的Liam和Noel Gallagher。学分：西蒙·埃米特（Simon Emmett）</figcaption></figure><p> Ticketmaster回应了<i>NME</i>对CMA调查的评论请求，他说：“在Ticketmaster，我们努力通过简单，透明和消费者友好的体验来提供最佳的售票平台。我们欢迎CMA的投入，以帮助使该行业更好地为粉丝们提供更好的售票。”</p><p>他们补充说，Ticketmaster“不使用&#39;动态定价&#39;，包括算法，差别或激增定价，我们很高兴CMA似乎从他们的调查中删除了这一点”。</p><p> CMA还指出，Ticketmaster已对其门票销售过程进行了一些更改，但他们说他们认为更改“足以解决”他们的担忧。</p><p>临时消费者保护高级总监海莉·弗莱彻（Hayley Fletcher）补充说：“我们担心Oasis粉丝没有得到他们所需的信息，或者可能被误导到购买他们认为比以前更好的门票。我们现在希望Ticketmaster能够与我们合作解决这些问题，因此，将来，购买门票时，粉丝将来可以做出明智的决定。”</p><p> CMA将从4月6日起拥有新的消费者权力，这将使他们能够决定何时破坏消费法，而无需将案件提交法院。新的数字市场，竞争和消费者2024年也将使他们能够罚款将消费者法违反其营业额的10％的公司。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-band-say-they-at-no-time-had-any-awareness-that-dynamic-pricing-was-going-to-be-used-3790679">Oasis表示，他们“从来没有意识到</a>要使用动态定价将要使用”。</p><p> In anticipation of the tour, which kicks off on July 4 in Cardiff, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-line-up-band-reunion-tour-members-2025-3845348">sources close to the band told <i>NME</i> that the band&#39;s line-up</a> will include <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/andy-bell">Andy Bell</a> , Gem Archer, Paul “Bonehead” Arthurs and Joey Waronker, alongside <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/noel-gallagher">Noel</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/liam-gallagher">Liam Gallagher</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/ticketmaster-may-have-breached-the-law-and-misled-fans-during-oasis-reunion-tour-ticket-sale-cma-warns-3849182">Ticketmaster may have “breached the law” and “misled fans” during Oasis reunion tour ticket sale, CMA warns</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
